The tremor also damaged at least 20 makeshift houses in Natore . Thousands of nervous people hurried out of their homes into the street in fear of aftershocks in Rajshahi , Lalmonirhat , Barisal , Brahmanbaria and Chapainawabganj . Four rental power plants in Tangail , Thakurgaon , Jessore and Syedpur went off for nearly 30 minutes on impact of the quake , said Saiful Hasan Chowdhury , director of public relations department of the Power Development Board . Nearly 300 miners at Baropukuria coal mine remained trapped for about 20 minutes for power failure caused by the quake .